<p><b>Iain Menzies Banks</b> (born on 16 February 1954 in <a href="/wiki/Dunfermline" title="Dunfermline">Dunfermline</a>, <a href="/wiki/Fife" title="Fife">Fife</a>) is a <a href="/wiki/Scottish_people" title="Scottish people">Scottish</a> <a href="/wiki/Writer" title="Writer">writer</a>. He writes mainstream fiction under his birth name <b>Iain Banks</b>, and <a href="/wiki/Science_fiction" title="Science fiction">science fiction</a> as <b>Iain M. Banks</b>, including his middle initial to differentiate between the genres.</p>
